00:06:56.790 --> 00:07:00.000
I think it would certainly
adversely affect the ability

00:07:00.000 --> 00:07:05.470
of software companies to
co-license, including the manner

00:07:05.470 --> 00:07:08.810
in which these software companies
license as well as their ability

00:07:08.810 --> 00:07:10.270
to enforce these licenses.

00:07:10.270 --> 00:07:13.160
As a result, it will be
more challenging for them

00:07:13.160 --> 00:07:16.000
to recoup their investment
they make to--

00:07:16.000 --> 00:07:21.560 position:56%
