00:07:34.470 --> 00:07:37.050
scope of warranties
and support services,

00:07:37.050 --> 00:07:39.470
I think could be adversely
affected as well.

00:07:39.470 --> 00:07:43.940
It almost certainly would
change their pricing structure,

00:07:43.940 --> 00:07:46.240
certainly given the
provisions on maintenance

00:07:46.240 --> 00:07:49.370
and support that are in the bill.

00:07:49.370 --> 00:07:53.700
And it could also allow
competitors to get access

00:07:53.700 --> 00:07:59.170
to their software more readily
