sufficient there?

00:08:17.040 --> 00:08:19.920
I mean, YODA doesn't
take away the ability

00:08:19.920 --> 00:08:23.270
to bring in infringement suit?

00:08:23.270 --> 00:08:25.110
&gt;&gt; Keith Kupferschmid:
So, yeah, no, I think--

00:08:25.110 --> 00:08:28.780 position:56%
I mean I think that's right, but
like I said, it would make it easier

00:08:28.780 --> 00:08:31.650
so I don't think you
