00:08:48.750 --> 00:08:51.460
&gt;&gt; Sy Damle: But do you think
the licenses are actually is--

00:08:51.460 --> 00:08:58.310
or what preventing
that's kind of theft?

00:08:58.310 --> 00:08:59.610
&gt;&gt; Keith Kupferschmid: I would hope

00:08:59.610 --> 00:09:02.610
to some extent that
that is the case.

00:09:02.610 --> 00:09:05.860 position:56%
I mean, certainly, well, like I
