from a consumer protection or from,

01:05:16.390 --> 01:05:20.660
you know, sort of satisfying
their customer base,

01:05:20.660 --> 01:05:22.930
I think it makes a lot of sense
for these software companies

01:05:22.930 --> 01:05:25.620
to includes a provision in there
that says, yes you can transfer.

01:05:25.620 --> 01:05:27.300
We're giving you-- That's
