01:05:27.300 --> 01:05:30.470
yes you can transfer the software
but under these circumstances

01:05:30.470 --> 01:05:33.550
which is we need to know who you're
transferring it to so we know

01:05:33.550 --> 01:05:37.590
who to deliver the consumer support
to the upgrades, the bug fixes.

01:05:37.590 --> 01:05:39.700
I think that's completely
